      "span_text": "Sheep were subject to clinical monitoring including standard daily observations, monthly bodyweight measurement and condition scoring, and monthly scratch response testing, and were euthanized using sodium barbiturate when they reached a clinical end point with signs characteristic of a TSE, as previously reported"
